    const float AGING_RATE = 3.0e-6; // 3ppm per year
float agingCorrection =
    AGING_RATE * (currentTime.totalSeconds / (365.25 * 24 * 3600));
```

    3. Periodic Synchronization :
```c void
    syncWithReference(uint32_t referenceTime) {
  int32_t timeDiff = referenceTime - currentTime.totalSeconds;
  if (abs(timeDiff) > 1) {
    // Log drift for analysis
    logTimeDrift(timeDiff);
    // Apply correction
    setTime(referenceTime);
  }
}
```

    4. Error Monitoring :
```c typedef struct {
